        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小曲） 四月里四月二十八，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘庙里把香插。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年纪不过刚二八："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "漆黑的头发红头绳儿扎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扬州的胭脂把脸蛋儿搽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "樱桃小口一点点大。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走一步，咯答答。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她可不住地叫她妈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你唱完了没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我唱完了，还没尽兴，我还要再乐一个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还唱什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（京调） 一更里进绣兰房，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "樱桃口呼唤声梅香："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对菱花卸去残妆，泪两行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听谯楼更鼓凄忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一纱窗月影，月照窗，窗棂上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。你再唱一出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再唱一出？你倒听出了瘾来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（玉美情人） 玉美呀情人病在床，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫了声冤家，快进奴的房，有话与你商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "低声悄语叫了声哥哥，你稳坐听奴家说："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今晚的病儿重加十分，要见五殿阎君。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿回家去娶上门子亲，传留后代根。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫娶烟花柳巷人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派地假殷勤，米汤可就灌死了人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我唱了这么半天，连一碗水都没有喝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么你就请进来坐坐，我与你去倒茶去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好好，我就到你里头去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我到里头去坐坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金铃大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等着，我去与你倒茶去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（金铃大仙下。猪八戒看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是个石头洞吓。这桌子上霞光万道，瑞气千条，这是什么东西？哎呀，敢自"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我到了妖怪家里来了。这不是魂铃么？待我偷了去，我趁着没人，我快逃走了"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒下。四小妖、二妖怪同追下。）"
        }
      ],
