    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空上，耍棍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "八戒前去盗魂铃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人声呐喊为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我命八戒去盗魂铃，这般时候不见到来，也不知何处呐喊，待俺空中一望。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空上桌，猪八戒上，妖怪、众小妖同追上，开打，猪八戒下，众人同追下。孙悟空下桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然是八戒与众妖魔争斗起来。待我拔些毫毛，变些子子孙孙与妖魔交战便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小猴执棍同上，教演，转场。众小妖、妖怪同上，起打。妖怪下。小猴童耍棍，拉下场，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1,
